PUB_ETH_ADDR not set: Check .env or wallet.txt, last line must be your wallet

Docker permission denied: sudo usermod -aG docker $USER + restart session

Node keeps restarting: Check logs or run ./restartWithCleanup.sh

Port conflicts: Default ports are 38131, 18545, 18546, 18150

Windows/WSL: Keep repo inside WSL filesystem (/home/user)
